refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.description;
public static intSwoole\Timer::after intmsec callablecallback_function mixedparams
Execute a function after a specified time. The Swoole\Timer::after function is a one-time timer that will be destroyed once executed.

  &reftitle.examples;



    Swoole\Timer::after example


<?php
$str = "Swoole";
Swoole\Timer::after(1000, function() use ($str) {
    echo "Hello, $str\n";
});
?>
